summary: This document appears to be a text message exchange arranging transportation for an individual to the Hilton West Palm Beach for a meeting. The sender provides logistical details about a Lyft ride and meeting in the lobby to proceed to a conference room.

events.title: Transportation Arranged for Hilton Meeting
events.description: A text message exchange arranges for a Lyft to transport an individual to the Hilton West Palm Beach for a meeting in a conference room.

keyFacts: A text message exchange on June 6, 2019, arranged transportation via Lyft to the Hilton West Palm Beach.
The purpose was to bring an individual to a conference room meeting at the hotel.
The sender planned to meet the individual in the hotel lobby upon arrival.
The message mentions 'running into some issues with the atm' suggesting a possible financial or logistical complication.
